    "description": "<p>\r\n\t<strong>M-TECH AIR-CON &amp; SECURITY ENGINEERING PTE LTD</strong> IS AN ESTABLISHED PRIVATE LIMITED COMPANY SINCE 24/06/1993. OUR CORE BUSINESS SERVICE IS TO PROVIDE AIR-CONDITIONING AND MECHANICAL VENTILATION (ACMV) SERVICES FOR RESIDENTIAL AND COMMERCIAL BUILDING. OUR VAST EXPERIENCES ENABLE US TO DESIGN, ADVISE, SUPPLY AND INSTALL A SYSTEM PERFECTLY SUITED TO CUSTOMER&#39;S REQUIREMENTS. SINCE OUR INCEPTION IN 1993 WE HAVE BUILT AN OUTSTANDING REPUTATION IN THE AIR CONDITIONING BUSINESS AND PROVIDED TIMELY, COST-EFFCTIVE AND PROFFESIONAL SERVICE FOR MANY LARGE ORGANIZATIONS.</p>\r\n",
